\c 5
\s Isivumelwano sikaSolomoni loHiramu
\p
\v 1 UHiramu inkosi yeTire wasethuma inceku zakhe kuSolomoni\x + Josh. 19.29. Amos 1.9.\x*, ngoba wayezwile ukuthi bamgcobile ukuthi abe yinkosi esikhundleni sikayise, ngoba uHiramu wayemthanda uDavida insuku zonke\x + 2 Sam. 5.11. 1 Lan. 14.1.\x*.
\v 2 USolomoni wasethumela kuHiramu esithi\x + 2 Lan. 2.3-16.\x*:
\v 3 Wena uyazi ukuthi uDavida ubaba wayengelakwakhela ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakhe indlu ngenxa yezimpi ezazimzingelezele, iN\nd kosi\nd* yaze yazifaka ngaphansi kwengaphansi yenyawo zakhe\x + 1 Lan. 22.8. 28.3.\x*.
\v 4 Kodwa khathesi iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu inginikile ukuphumula inhlangothi zonke\x + 4.24. 1 Lan. 22.9.\x*; kakulasitha, njalo kakulabubi obenzakalayo\x + Tshu. 9.11.\x*.
\v 5 Khangela-ke, ngizimisele ukwakhela ibizo leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wami indlu njengokutsho kweN\nd kosi\nd* kuDavida ubaba isithi: Indodana yakho engizayibeka esihlalweni sakho sobukhosi esikhundleni sakho, yona izakwakhela ibizo lami indlu\x + 1 Lan. 28.6.\x*.
\v 6 Ngakho-ke laya ukuthi bangigamulele imisedari eLebhanoni, lenceku zami zizakuba lenceku zakho; leholo lenceku zakho ngizakunika njengakho konke okutshoyo. Ngoba wena uyakwazi ukuthi kakho phakathi kwethu okwaziyo ukugamula izihlahla njengabeSidoni\x + Gen. 10.15. 1 Lan. 22.4.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Kwasekusithi uHiramu esizwa amazwi kaSolomoni wathokoza kakhulu wathi: Kayibusiswe iN\nd kosi\nd* lamuhla emnikileyo uDavida indodana ehlakaniphileyo phezu kwalesisizwe esikhulu\x + 10.9.\x*.
\v 8 UHiramu wasethumela kuSolomoni esithi: Ngizwile lokho ongithumele ngakho; mina ngizakwenza zonke iziloyiso zakho mayelana lezigodo zemisedari lamayelana lezigodo \w zamafiri\w**\x + 5.10. 6.15,34. 2 Sam. 6.5. 2 Lan. 3.5. Isa. 14.8. Hez. 27.5.\x*.
\v 9 Inceku zami zizazehlisa zisuka eLebhanoni zisiya elwandle; mina-ke ngizazenza okundendayo olwandle ukuya endaweni ozayiqamba kimi, ngizithukulule lapho; wena-ke uzazithathela khona, wena uzakwenza isifiso sami ngokupha abendlu yami ukudla\x + Ezra 3.7. Hez. 27.17. Seb. 12.20.\x*.
\v 10 Ngakho uHiramu wamnika uSolomoni izigodo zemisedari lezigodo zamafiri \add njengokwe\add*zifiso zakhe zonke.
\v 11 LoSolomoni wanika uHiramu \w amakhori\w** engqoloyi azinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu lambili, ukudla kwabendlu yakhe, \w lamakhori\w** angamatshumi amabili amafutha akhanyiweyo. Ngokunjalo uSolomoni wamupha uHiramu iminyaka ngeminyaka\x + 2 Lan. 2.10.\x*.
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasimnika uSolomoni inhlakanipho njengokutsho kwayo kuye. Kwasekusiba khona ukuthula phakathi kukaHiramu loSolomoni; benza isivumelwano bobabili\x + 3.12.\x*.
\p
\v 13 Inkosi uSolomoni yabutha izibhalwa kuIsrayeli wonke; lezibhalwa zazingabantu abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amathathu.
\v 14 Yasibathuma eLebhanoni, abazinkulungwane ezilitshumi ngenyanga ngamazopho, inyanga beseLebhanoni, inyanga ezimbili besekhaya. LoAdoniramu wayephezu kwezibhalwa\x + 4.6.\x*.
\v 15 Futhi uSolomoni wayelabayizinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisikhombisa abathwala imithwalo, lababazi abazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi ayisificaminwembili ezintabeni\x + 9.20-22. 2 Lan. 2.2,18. 2 Lan. 2.17.\x*,
\v 16 ngaphandle kwezinduna zabaphathi bakaSolomoni, ababephethe umsebenzi\x + 4.5.\x*, izinkulungwane ezintathu lamakhulu amathathu\x + 9.20-22. 2 Lan. 2.2,18. 2 Lan. 2.17.\x*, ezazibusa abantu ababesenza umsebenzi\x + 9.23.\x*.
\v 17 Inkosi yasilaya, baletha amatshe amakhulu, amatshe aligugu, okubeka isisekelo sendlu, amatshe abaziweyo\x + 6.7. 1 Lan. 22.2.\x*.
\v 18 Abakhi bakaSolomoni labakhi bakaHiramu lamaGebhali basebebaza, balungisa izigodo lamatshe ukwakha indlu.